 .../arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7987a-bananapi-bpi-r4-lite.dts | 5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)

--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7987a-bananapi-bpi-r4-lite.dts
